{"tid":2039110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美眾院首次代理遠距投票413:1 通過因新疆問題制裁中國官員","createTime":"2020-05-28T00:40:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T02:38:19.000Z","uid":141151,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7e921d0fa92b7fce00f754a74fcbfaca89560c2e","tid":2039110,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T00:40:46.000Z","msg":"美眾院首次代理遠距投票413:1 通過因新疆問題制裁中國官員<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4595796?from=udn-catebreaknews_ch2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F4595796%3Ffrom%3Dudn-catebreaknews_ch2&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PvUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=ade2c566\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4595796?from=udn-catebreaknews_ch2</a><br />\n<br />\n美國眾議院周三（27日）首次進行代理遠距投票，儘管共和黨領袖認為此舉違背200多年眾院慣例，已在周二興訟挑戰合憲性。<br />\n<br />\n這項新體制可由代理人投票，主要由包括眾院議長波洛西在內多位民主黨籍議員推動，他們認為，在不適合旅行的新冠肺炎疫情期間，此一臨時性措施可讓議員全員參與。<br />\n<br />\n眾院27日以413票對1票通過決議案，呼籲就新疆地區少數民族維吾爾人遭遇高壓待遇對中國大陸官員採取制裁，有69張贊成票由代理人投下。"},{"pid":"881cbad8fcd43087493f78e3f313f32ca9c27e55","tid":2039110,"uid":124983,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T00:43:09.000Z","msg":"又係果條蛋散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1e165200666823e59b64906273414fdfb96dfd","tid":2039110,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T00:43:27.000Z","msg":"五毛放負送頭投降撚，始終唔肯接受現實，消息無論好壞，一定係佢嬴我地輸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2039109\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2039109</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0282a8f184726e9621c0148ced9290bb95fd97bd","tid":2039110,"uid":105833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T00:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3917505fffd13e36be021f0a79231c88a00b17","tid":2039110,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T00